[2024-01-07 22:40:17] 我: If we’re all wrong, all the time, then isn’t self-skepticism and the rigorous challenging of our own beliefs and assumptions the only logical route to progress?

[2024-01-08 14:14:02] 我: Improvement at anything is based on thousands
[2024-01-08 14:16:47] 我: and the magnitude of your success is based on how many times you’ve failed at something.
